{
  "video_id": "RMF82fz4kDk",
  "title": "World of Tanks - Explaining Mechanics: Visibility System",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 5600.0,
      "end_time": 8132.0,
      "text": "Someone is a true born racer."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 9633.0,
      "end_time": 12466.0,
      "text": "Someone is a gifted sniper."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 13433.0,
      "end_time": 16300.0,
      "text": "Someone soaks up damage like Chuck Norris."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 17670.0,
      "end_time": 19367.0,
      "text": "And someone is just… A WINNER IN LIFE!"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23200.0,
      "end_time": 26533.0,
      "text": "But you don’t need to be that cool to play tanks well."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28133.0,
      "end_time": 30700.0,
      "text": "It’s enough to understand the game mechanics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31200.0,
      "end_time": 34400.0,
      "text": "know how they work, and use this knowledge in battle."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35670.0,
      "end_time": 38767.0,
      "text": "I’ll talk about the mechanics, and the rest is up to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 58500.0,
      "end_time": 60567.0,
      "text": "THE VISIBILITY SYSTEM."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 60867.0,
      "end_time": 62132.0,
      "text": "A keystone."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 62467.0,
      "end_time": 64867.0,
      "text": "The giant turtle that holds up the Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 65200.0,
      "end_time": 66700.0,
      "text": "You may not believe in it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 66800.0,
      "end_time": 68500.0,
      "text": "you may be surprised by it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 68867.0,
      "end_time": 70800.0,
      "text": "you may argue about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 71233.0,
      "end_time": 74167.0,
      "text": "But whether you like it or not, it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 75133.0,
      "end_time": 77600.0,
      "text": "And smart tankers have used its features"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 77700.0,
      "end_time": 80400.0,
      "text": "for their benefit for a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 81867.0,
      "end_time": 83233.0,
      "text": "Roughly speaking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 83333.0,
      "end_time": 85300.0,
      "text": "the visibility system in World of Tanks"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 85400.0,
      "end_time": 88833.0,
      "text": "can be divided into two, though inseparable, components:"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 89400.0,
      "end_time": 91333.0,
      "text": "concealment and view range."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 91833.0,
      "end_time": 94133.0,
      "text": "Today we’ll talk about view range."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 95300.0,
      "end_time": 97167.0,
      "text": "A little bit of theory to begin."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 97900.0,
      "end_time": 100700.0,
      "text": "Our confidential informant will tell you about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 101533.0,
      "end_time": 102800.0,
      "text": "Every tank in the game"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 102900.0,
      "end_time": 107660.0,
      "text": "has seven visibility checkpoints and two view range ports."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 107566.0,
      "end_time": 110133.0,
      "text": "The latter are needed to spot enemy vehicles."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 110800.0,
      "end_time": 113566.0,
      "text": "These ports emit virtual vision rays."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 113866.0,
      "end_time": 115166.0,
      "text": "If these rays cross"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 115266.0,
      "end_time": 117400.0,
      "text": "the visibility checkpoints on the enemy vehicles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 117500.0,
      "end_time": 119666.0,
      "text": "then an enemy is spotted."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 120660.0,
      "end_time": 122200.0,
      "text": "To understand the location of these points better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 122300.0,
      "end_time": 124633.0,
      "text": "imagine your favorite vehicle…"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 128633.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131366.0,
      "text": "And now we’ll cover it with a box!"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 131800.0,
      "end_time": 133466.0,
      "text": "Turret location, gun length,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 133566.0,
      "end_time": 137330.0,
      "text": "machine guns, and antennas don’t affect the box size."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 139533.0,
      "end_time": 142333.0,
      "text": "Only the overall size of the vehicle’s physics model"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 142433.0,
      "end_time": 144266.0,
      "text": "is taken into account."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 144966.0,
      "end_time": 148700.0,
      "text": "So, there’s a checkpoint right at the center of the box roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 150433.0,
      "end_time": 151500.0,
      "text": "Two more checkpoints"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 151600.0,
      "end_time": 154200.0,
      "text": "are located at the front and at the back of the vehicle."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 154400.0,
      "end_time": 156166.0,
      "text": "Another two are at the sides."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 156433.0,
      "end_time": 157965.0,
      "text": "So that’s five."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 158800.0,
      "end_time": 160900.0,
      "text": "The sixth point is on the gun mantlet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 161000.0,
      "end_time": 163660.0,
      "text": "and it’s aligned with the seventh."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 163333.0,
      "end_time": 166233.0,
      "text": "As soon as the turret position changes, one of these points"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 166333.0,
      "end_time": 170466.0,
      "text": "moves together with the mantlet, and the other stays in place."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 173166.0,
      "end_time": 175766.0,
      "text": "The upper checkpoint and the point on the gun mantlet"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 175866.0,
      "end_time": 178400.0,
      "text": "also function as view range ports."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 179330.0,
      "end_time": 179965.0,
      "text": "Hey-hey-hey!"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 180300.0,
      "end_time": 181400.0,
      "text": "Easy!"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 181700.0,
      "end_time": 185299.0,
      "text": "Theory is good, but how do you use it in the battle?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 186300.0,
      "end_time": 188700.0,
      "text": "Let’s see some specific examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 189400.0,
      "end_time": 191660.0,
      "text": "You’re standing behind cover."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 191166.0,
      "end_time": 194233.0,
      "text": "Allies are behind you, the enemy is ahead."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 194600.0,
      "end_time": 196666.0,
      "text": "Some are asking you to light them up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 196766.0,
      "end_time": 198866.0,
      "text": "others are waiting for free damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 198966.0,
      "end_time": 203833.0,
      "text": "In a situation like this, don’t try to spot the enemy this way"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 204666.0,
      "end_time": 206166.0,
      "text": "You’re exposing your checkpoint,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 206266.0,
      "end_time": 208533.0,
      "text": "but your view ports are still behind cover."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 208966.0,
      "end_time": 213000.0,
      "text": "You’ve got yourself spotted, but haven’t spotted the enemy."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 213733.0,
      "end_time": 216133.0,
      "text": "And you’ve also taken a lot of damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 217766.0,
      "end_time": 219600.0,
      "text": "This is how you should do it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 220433.0,
      "end_time": 223866.0,
      "text": "turn your turret and carefully try to spot the enemy"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 225333.0,
      "end_time": 227500.0,
      "text": "with your view port on the gun mantlet."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 228466.0,
      "end_time": 234700.0,
      "text": "Your allies fire off, you save your HP, and receive a bonus for spotting."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 235733.0,
      "end_time": 237300.0,
      "text": "Everyone is happy!"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 239500.0,
      "end_time": 242533.0,
      "text": "Another example: You don’t need to rush in"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 242633.0,
      "end_time": 245733.0,
      "text": "and spot the enemy first, it’s pretty risky."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 246666.0,
      "end_time": 249500.0,
      "text": "Sure, you’ll see them, but you won’t last long."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 251600.0,
      "end_time": 253900.0,
      "text": "To be a good scout and keep yourself safe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 254000.0,
      "end_time": 256330.0,
      "text": "you can stay on your side of the hill."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 256233.0,
      "end_time": 258666.0,
      "text": "You just need to roll up the hill"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 258766.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260966.00000000003,
      "text": "and point your turret in the right direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 261565.0,
      "end_time": 263166.0,
      "text": "The view range port in the gun base"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 263266.0,
      "end_time": 268660.0,
      "text": "will give you all the information, and you almost don’t risk anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 269633.0,
      "end_time": 270900.0,
      "text": "Let’s move forward:"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 271433.0,
      "end_time": 273233.0,
      "text": "Two scouts are hiding in the bushes."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 273766.0,
      "end_time": 275866.0,
      "text": "The first is spotting, and the other is…"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 275966.0,
      "end_time": 278000.0,
      "text": "The other is being spotted!"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 279833.0,
      "end_time": 280966.0,
      "text": "But, not for long."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 281660.0,
      "end_time": 283866.0,
      "text": "That’s because it didn’t hide its checkpoint."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 286366.0,
      "end_time": 289800.0,
      "text": "The first tank exposes its gun, machine gun, antenna,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 289900.0,
      "end_time": 291765.0,
      "text": "and even the corners of the hull itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 292433.0,
      "end_time": 294000.0,
      "text": "but it doesn’t matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 294533.0,
      "end_time": 297766.0,
      "text": "What matters is that all checkpoints are covered."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 298400.0,
      "end_time": 301465.0,
      "text": "It provides good spotting and is still intact."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 302266.0,
      "end_time": 306366.0,
      "text": "See, that’s what knowing the game mechanics can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 307700.0,
      "end_time": 309633.0,
      "text": "By the way, about the mechanics!"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 309933.0,
      "end_time": 311933.0,
      "text": "Vision rays are not endless."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 312300.0,
      "end_time": 316500.0,
      "text": "The maximum view or spotting range is 445 meters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 316600.0,
      "end_time": 321000.0,
      "text": "and the maximum draw distance is 565 meters."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 321233.0,
      "end_time": 324300.0,
      "text": "You need to understand the difference between these terms."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 324600.0,
      "end_time": 328333.0,
      "text": "View range is the maximum distance at which you can spot the enemy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 328433.0,
      "end_time": 331660.0,
      "text": "and the draw distance is the maximum distance"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 331166.0,
      "end_time": 334366.0,
      "text": "at which you can see the vehicles in general."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 335133.0,
      "end_time": 336633.0,
      "text": "Both allied vehicles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 336733.0,
      "end_time": 339900.0,
      "text": "and enemy vehicles spotted by your team."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 341166.0,
      "end_time": 343533.0,
      "text": "Depending on the distance between vehicles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 343633.0,
      "end_time": 346500.0,
      "text": "the vision rays have different frequencies."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 346733.0,
      "end_time": 350766.0,
      "text": "The highest frequency is at a distance of 120 meters."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 351330.0,
      "end_time": 353633.0,
      "text": "The greater the distance between vehicles is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 354000.0,
      "end_time": 357233.0,
      "text": "the lower the frequency of rays will be."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 358833.0,
      "end_time": 361433.0,
      "text": "And now let’s get some practice in!"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 362660.0,
      "end_time": 364500.0,
      "text": "There are three circles on your minimap."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 364800.0,
      "end_time": 367100.0,
      "text": "The big circle shows the draw area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 367566.0,
      "end_time": 370599.0,
      "text": "the middle circle shows the maximum view range area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 371000.0,
      "end_time": 374566.0,
      "text": "and the small circle shows the current view range of your vehicle."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 374700.0,
      "end_time": 376765.0,
      "text": "These are not JUST circles."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 377433.0,
      "end_time": 381866.0,
      "text": "These are important game tools, and you need to use them!"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 382933.0,
      "end_time": 384332.0,
      "text": "Every time you shoot at the enemy"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 384433.0,
      "end_time": 386633.0,
      "text": "within the maximum view range circle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 386733.0,
      "end_time": 388500.0,
      "text": "you risk being spotted."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 388600.0,
      "end_time": 391100.0,
      "text": "With all enraging consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 393300.0,
      "end_time": 394566.0,
      "text": "To shoot with impunity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 394666.0,
      "end_time": 397900.0,
      "text": "roll back out of the maximum view range circle."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 398566.0,
      "end_time": 401433.0,
      "text": "The enemy won’t be able to spot you even theoretically."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 402100.0,
      "end_time": 405166.0,
      "text": "But you can do some damage and save your HP."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 407200.0,
      "end_time": 408366.0,
      "text": "But that’s not all."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 409660.0,
      "end_time": 411166.0,
      "text": "If the enemy vehicle is so far away"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 411266.0,
      "end_time": 413666.0,
      "text": "that you can see it only on the minimap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 414166.0,
      "end_time": 416332.0,
      "text": "it doesn’t mean you’re out of play."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 416700.0,
      "end_time": 420166.0,
      "text": "You can guestimate the direction of fire on the minimap."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 420500.0,
      "end_time": 422533.0,
      "text": "To do so, use the pointer."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 423233.0,
      "end_time": 424433.0,
      "text": "When the sector is defined,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 424533.0,
      "end_time": 428200.0,
      "text": "you look through your sight at the most probable enemy location."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 428600.0,
      "end_time": 430833.0,
      "text": "Fire…  And bingo!"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 431400.0,
      "end_time": 432765.0,
      "text": "Isn’t that beautiful?"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 432866.0,
      "end_time": 435800.0,
      "text": "Of course, you won’t land a hit with every shot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 436266.0,
      "end_time": 439533.0,
      "text": "but I love Tanks for the moments like this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 441700.0,
      "end_time": 443700.0,
      "text": "Also, remember one simple thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 444233.0,
      "end_time": 448660.0,
      "text": "No tank in the game has a maxed out view range to begin with."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 448866.0,
      "end_time": 452866.0,
      "text": "To be a really cool scout, you need to upgrade your ride."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 457330.0,
      "end_time": 458666.0,
      "text": "This is down to you alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 459200.0,
      "end_time": 460500.0,
      "text": "You choose for yourself"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 460600.0,
      "end_time": 464266.0,
      "text": "what to equip your vehicle with and how to train your crew."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 465400.0,
      "end_time": 467660.0,
      "text": "DON’T SCREW IT UP!"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 468660.0,
      "end_time": 471200.0,
      "text": "Documentation shows the initial vehicle characteristics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 471300.0,
      "end_time": 472466.0,
      "text": "assuming that it’s manned"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 472566.0,
      "end_time": 476500.0,
      "text": "with a 100% trained crew without any additional skills and perks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 476600.0,
      "end_time": 479633.0,
      "text": "and there’s no equipment or consumables on the vehicle."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 482266.0,
      "end_time": 486733.0,
      "text": "To improve your view range fully, you first need to equip your vehicle"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 486833.0,
      "end_time": 489700.0,
      "text": "with Coated Optics or Binocular Telescope."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 489800.0,
      "end_time": 491800.0,
      "text": "In some cases, you can mount both."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 491900.0,
      "end_time": 493166.0,
      "text": "But keep in mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 493266.0,
      "end_time": 496500.0,
      "text": "bonuses from these pieces of equipment are not totaled."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 496600.0,
      "end_time": 500666.0,
      "text": "When stationary, you get an additional 25% to your view range,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 500766.0,
      "end_time": 502600.0,
      "text": "in motion—10%."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 502766.0,
      "end_time": 505133.0,
      "text": "Secondly, you need to train your crew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 505233.0,
      "end_time": 506966.0,
      "text": "Especially, your Commander."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 507660.0,
      "end_time": 509660.0,
      "text": "Every additional 1 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 509166.0,
      "end_time": 511200.0,
      "text": "of the Commander’s major qualification"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 511300.0,
      "end_time": 515100.0,
      "text": "improves the vehicle view range by 0.43%."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 515433.0,
      "end_time": 517299.0,
      "text": "To enhance the main qualification,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 517400.0,
      "end_time": 520330.0,
      "text": "you need to equip your vehicle with Ventilation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 520133.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522200.00000000006,
      "text": "the national food or drink consumable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 522299.0,
      "end_time": 525320.0,
      "text": "and train your crew with the Brothers-in-Arms perk."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 525133.0,
      "end_time": 526300.0,
      "text": "Also, it would be good"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 526400.0,
      "end_time": 528433.0,
      "text": "to train the Commander with the Recon skill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 528533.0,
      "end_time": 532400.0,
      "text": "and the Radio Operator with the Situational Awareness skill."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 532500.0,
      "end_time": 534933.0,
      "text": "And don’t forget about Sixth Sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 535166.0,
      "end_time": 537666.0,
      "text": "This is one of your main allies in the battle."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 537766.0,
      "end_time": 539533.0,
      "text": "If the enemy spots your vehicle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 539633.0,
      "end_time": 542666.0,
      "text": "you’ll receive the alert about it in 3 seconds."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 542866.0,
      "end_time": 546665.0,
      "text": "Ignoring it will make your trip to the Garage arrive sooner."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 548700.0,
      "end_time": 550600.0,
      "text": "This is all well and good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 550800.0,
      "end_time": 553733.0,
      "text": "but sometimes three seconds is too long!"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 555200.0,
      "end_time": 558366.0,
      "text": "And you also have your brain, not just the light bulb!"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 558733.0,
      "end_time": 560000.0,
      "text": "So use it!"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 560333.0,
      "end_time": 562466.0,
      "text": "If you feel you might have been spotted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 562566.0,
      "end_time": 563833.0,
      "text": "don’t wait for the light bulb,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 563933.0,
      "end_time": 566266.0,
      "text": "roll back to a safe place beforehand!"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 566366.0,
      "end_time": 568199.0,
      "text": "Your crew won’t exactly say “thank you”,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 568300.0,
      "end_time": 571766.0,
      "text": "but their gratitude will certainly show itself later on."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 572533.0,
      "end_time": 574400.0,
      "text": "Remember that if your Commander is injured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 574500.0,
      "end_time": 576666.0,
      "text": "their Sixth Sense doesn’t work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 576933.0,
      "end_time": 579300.0,
      "text": "and your vision range drops by half."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 579733.0,
      "end_time": 582866.0,
      "text": "In this case, any enemy will “out-scout” you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 583266.0,
      "end_time": 587650.0,
      "text": "so don’t even try to spot them, the result is pretty obvious."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 588433.0,
      "end_time": 589665.0,
      "text": "When the tank is equipped"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 589766.0,
      "end_time": 592266.0,
      "text": "with all the necessary equipment and consumables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 593400.0,
      "end_time": 595665.0,
      "text": "when the crew is trained, the numbers say"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 595766.0,
      "end_time": 599733.0,
      "text": "that the vehicle view range can exceed 500 meters!"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 600700.0,
      "end_time": 604366.0,
      "text": "But the maximum view range in the game is…445."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 605333.0,
      "end_time": 609699.0,
      "text": "So why do you need all those skills, equipment, and consumables?"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 610166.0,
      "end_time": 613900.0,
      "text": "It seems that you can just raise it to the maximum and stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 614233.0,
      "end_time": 615965.0,
      "text": "But things aren’t that simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 616133.0,
      "end_time": 617700.0,
      "text": "Let’s do a small experiment:"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 617833.0,
      "end_time": 621366.0,
      "text": "Let’s take two scouts, identical at first glance."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 621466.0,
      "end_time": 624266.0,
      "text": "But the view range of the first one is 445 meters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 624366.0,
      "end_time": 627133.0,
      "text": "and the second scout has a view range of 507 m."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 628800.0,
      "end_time": 631233.0,
      "text": "There are several enemy vehicles behind the hill."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 631400.0,
      "end_time": 634100.0,
      "text": "The first scout rolls out and shows us four tanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 634366.0,
      "end_time": 635866.0,
      "text": "Well, not bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 636966.0,
      "end_time": 639866.0,
      "text": "Now let’s see how many vehicles the second scout will spot?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 641500.0,
      "end_time": 643133.0,
      "text": "Wow, it’s just amazing!"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 643966.0,
      "end_time": 645733.0,
      "text": "It lit them up like a Christmas tree!"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 645833.0,
      "end_time": 646966.0,
      "text": "Ten!"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 647233.0,
      "end_time": 648800.0,
      "text": "TEN VEHICLES!"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 649466.0,
      "end_time": 651400.0,
      "text": "And it’s not a bug or an accident!"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 652166.0,
      "end_time": 654600.0,
      "text": "That’s the tank’s improved view range!"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 656733.0,
      "end_time": 660990.0,
      "text": "Every extra meter of the view range is very useful."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 661660.0,
      "end_time": 664233.0,
      "text": "It sees straight through the enemy’s camouflage."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 666500.0,
      "end_time": 670100.0,
      "text": "To reinforce its importance, let’s do another experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 671333.0,
      "end_time": 674466.0,
      "text": "Let’s take the same scouts and put them on the Airfield map."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 675000.0,
      "end_time": 677000.0,
      "text": "The crew isn’t trained with Camouflage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 677100.0,
      "end_time": 679433.0,
      "text": "and there’s no camo on the tank either."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 680333.0,
      "end_time": 683366.0,
      "text": "So, neither have any advantage in concealment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 683866.0,
      "end_time": 686800.0,
      "text": "everything depends purely on their view range."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 688000.0,
      "end_time": 690366.0,
      "text": "Now let the tanks move towards each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 690466.0,
      "end_time": 694000.0,
      "text": "and we’ll see what distance they get each other in their sights."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 697833.0,
      "end_time": 700833.0,
      "text": "The RU 251, with a view range of 507 meters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 700933.0,
      "end_time": 704165.0,
      "text": "spots the enemy at 427 meters."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 705400.0,
      "end_time": 707933.0,
      "text": "And its opponent hasn’t seen anyone yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 713600.0,
      "end_time": 716366.0,
      "text": "And only now, after the precious seconds are gone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 716700.0,
      "end_time": 718333.0,
      "text": "it’s finally spotted."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 719200.0,
      "end_time": 722166.0,
      "text": "The rangefinder shows 375 meters."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 722433.0,
      "end_time": 723533.0,
      "text": "But why is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 723633.0,
      "end_time": 725766.0,
      "text": "Shouldn’t it be 445?"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 727466.0,
      "end_time": 729400.0,
      "text": "That’s because every vehicle in the game"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 729500.0,
      "end_time": 732900.0,
      "text": "also has concealment parameters, not just a view range."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 733266.0,
      "end_time": 736165.0,
      "text": "The vehicle’s concealment is affected by the vehicle type,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 736266.0,
      "end_time": 739433.0,
      "text": "size, and presence of special equipment and consumables."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 740200.0,
      "end_time": 744660.0,
      "text": "Vehicle concealment gets worse when firing and on the move."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 745333.0,
      "end_time": 748433.0,
      "text": "But we’ll tell you about that in the next episode."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 749330.0,
      "end_time": 750533.0,
      "text": "And that’s all for today."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 750633.0,
      "end_time": 753400.0,
      "text": "Use these mechanics and win more!"
    }
  ]
}